'''''Current Medical Research and Opinion''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] established in 1972. It is published monthly by [[Informa]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
The journal is abstracted and indexed by [[MEDLINE]]/[[PubMed]], [[EMBASE|EMBASE/Excerpta Medica]], [[Current Contents]]/Clinical Medicine, [[Science Citation Index]], [[CAB Direct (database)|CAB Abstracts]], [[PASCAL (database)|PASCAL]], and [[PsycINFO]]. According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal's 2009 [[impact factor]] is 2.498.

